imdb.plot outline: WHAT HAVE I GOT? is an all-new, 12-part original series that explores medical anomalies in a mystery diagnosis format that encourages viewers to play the doctor alongside the show's experts. In each episode of WHAT HAVE I GOT?, viewers meet three ordinary individuals with uncanny medical conditions. Sometimes emotional, other times humorous, and always captivating, these individuals reveal their symptoms in a series of carefully crafted clues.
